high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the coffee maker on your left.
Pick up the black cup on the coffee maker.
Turn left and walk towards the microwave at the left corner from you.
Warm up the cup inside the microwave and take it back out.
Turn around, walk towards the stove, and then make a left towards the coffee maker.
Place the cup back on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Warm up the cup on the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn to your right and head to the coffee maker
Pick up the cup from the coffee maker
Turn to your left and head towards the microwave
Open the microwave, put the cup in, then open the microwave again
Head to back to the coffee maker
Put the cup back to the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Heat the cup to the microwave going back to the coffee maker

high_descs: Turn right and go to the coffee maker.
Turn left and go to the microwave.
Put the mug in the microwave and heat it.
Turn around and carry the mug back to the coffee maker.
Put the mug on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Heat the mug on the coffee maker.
